rComments: Best profesor I've had in my academic career at Ottawa U. Brilliant, passionate, and knows his stuff. If you can, don't hesitate to take a class with this professor. You won't regret it, trust me.
Very brilliant teacher and kind man. Fair marker.
Best prof i've ever had! Cool dude and totally smart. UOttawa should have more like him. He treats his students like equals and rejects conventional teaching methods. Definitely take his class!

Arne is one cool dude! I wish UOttawa fired half their staff and made a bunch of Arne clones. He always gives you the straight goods when you ask questions. Kind of like Gwenn Dyer.. Lectures are fun and informative. Sometimes he can get a bit carried away in explanation though and ramble a bit. Enfin, I would definitely recommend taking his class!

Arne Rueckert is a great prof! He knows his stuff, is helpful during office hours and teaches with a wide diversity of materials! He caters to each student's interest as well! There was no coursepack or textbook, all the articles were available online! FANTASTIC PROF
